"w2_q56x2"	"5"	"I feel uncomfortable in the presence of people I don't know"
"w2_q56x3"	"Variable Label"	"UNCERTAINTY TOLERANCE: LIFE EVENTS"
"w2_q56x3"	"1"	"I prefer to know what to expect in life"
"w2_q56x3"	"5"	"I like unexpected surprises in my life"
"w2_q56x4"	"Variable Label"	"UNCERTAINTY TOLERANCE: NEW/FAMILIAR SITUATIONS"
"w2_q56x4"	"1"	"I can deal well with situations that are unpredictable"
"w2_q56x4"	"5"	"I prefer to go into a situation knowing what I can expect from it"
"w2_q56x5"	"Variable Label"	"UNCERTAINTY TOLERANCE: CHANGING OPINIONS"
"w2_q56x5"	"1"	"I dislike it when people constantly change their mind"
"w2_q56x5"	"5"	"I think it is alright if people change their mind"
"w2_q56x6"	"Variable Label"	"UNCERTAINTY TOLERANCE: DISCUSSING DELICATE ISSUES"
